last type - function

set of instructions that takes an input and modifies it to yeild an output

it IS a data type with a literal syntax:

function(){
	
}

function must be defines and invoked to do anything.  

to STORE data, use return vs console.log and assign to variable.

can NAME function or name variable tied to ANONYMOUS function.  see js.

NAMED function can be called prior to the definition of the function - "hoisting"

***  Built in methods.  ex push with array 

	Strings - toUpperCase () toLowerCase() split('x')
	Arrays - join(' ') split()

SCOPE

	environments - where variables exist or don't exist

functions create scope.  